    Parameters:
        cloud_source: dict with 'points' (Nx3) and 'covariances' (Nx3x3)
        cloud_target: dict with 'points' (Mx3) and 'covariances' (Mx3x3)
        T_init: initial transformation (4x4)
    
    Returns:
        T_opt: optimal transformation (4x4)
